                            <p align="left"><span style="color: red; mso-fareast-font-family: Times New Roman; mso-bidi-font-size: 13.5pt; mso-ansi-language: DE; mso-fareast-language: DE; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA"><a href="http://www.klimaforschung.net/haarp/index.htm#Eisschmelze"><font color="#800000"><b>LINK
                            ZU:</b> <font size="3">Das HAARP-Projekt - ein
